longBusinessSummary: HighGold Mining Inc., an exploration company, engages in the exploration and development of gold projects located in North America. It also explores for copper, zinc, silver, gold, and lead, as well as other base metals. The company's flagship asset is the 21,000-acre Johnson Tract gold property located in southcentral Alaska, the United States. HighGold Mining Inc. was founded in 2019 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
